name: fx-private-relay
description: Keep your email safe from hackers and trackers. Make an email alias with 1 click, and keep your address to yourself.

scripts.build:dev: npm run build:clean && sed -i '' 's/:8000//g'  manifest.json js/background.js popup.html && sed -i '' 's@http://127.0.0.1@https://dev.fxprivaterelay.nonprod.cloudops.mozgcp.net@g' manifest.json js/background.js popup.html && npm run build
scripts.build:stage: npm run build:clean && sed -i '' 's/:8000//g'  manifest.json js/background.js popup.html && sed -i '' 's@http://127.0.0.1@https://stage.fxprivaterelay.nonprod.cloudops.mozgcp.net@g' manifest.json js/background.js popup.html && npm run build
scripts.build:prod: npm run build:clean && sed -i '' 's/:8000//g'  manifest.json js/background.js popup.html && sed -i '' 's@http://127.0.0.1@https://relay.firefox.com@g' manifest.json js/background.js popup.html && npm run build

pkg.name: fx-private-relay
pkg.description: Private Relay provides generated email addresses to use in place of personal email addresses.
pkg.author: Mozilla
